fields.title: NetBIOS Name Accessible
fields.impact: Unauthorized users can obtain this host's NetBIOS server name from a remote system.

fields.title: NetBIOS Bindings Information
fields.impact: The following bindings were detected on this computer. Bindings have many purposes. They reflect such things as users logged-in, registration of a user name, registration of a service in a domain, and registering of a NetBIOS name.
